would have emigrated.

00:07:15.300 --> 00:07:18.240 align:middle line:84%
As this portion of
Atlantis was going down,

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:21.240 align:middle line:84%
they would have emigrated
over toward the land,

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:23.040 align:middle line:84%
toward Portugal, toward
the coast, right?

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:23.320 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: Yes.

00:07:23.320 --> 00:07:25.028 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: The closest
coastline, now it's

00:07:25.028 --> 00:07:28.320 align:middle line:84%
