the druidic knowledge, right?

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:37.110 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: And the Yucatan.

00:07:37.110 --> 00:07:39.690 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And the Yucatan
in the opposite direction,

00:07:39.690 --> 00:07:42.995 align:middle line:84%
again, seeded with the same
high, high knowledge, right?

00:07:42.995 --> 00:07:45.120 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: And the thing that
links them all together

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:47.700 align:middle line:84%
