>>REGINA: Found it.

00:14:28.280 --> 00:14:28.550 align:middle line:90%
Found it.

00:14:28.550 --> 00:14:30.060 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: And they're
going, what has he found?

00:14:30.060 --> 00:14:31.790 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, this is
going to change history.

00:14:31.790 --> 00:14:32.830 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know this
was even here.

00:14:32.830 --> 00:14:34.490 align:middle line:84%
So, yeah, it's a
bit of blind luck

00:14:34.490 --> 00:14:36.800 align:middle line:84%
but also a bit of intuition
and just following it.

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:37.740 align:middle line:90%
And see where it goes.

00:14:37.740 --> 00:14:40.550 align:middle line:84%
And once you tap into it,
and if you just, you know,

00:14:40.550 --> 00:14:44.390 align:middle line:84%
get out of your own way, don't
get moved by ego or anything,

00:14:44.390 --> 00:14:46.700 align:middle line:84%
it's amazing how much work
and how quickly things move.

00:14:46.700 --> 00:14:46.815 align:middle line:90%


00:14:46.815 --> 00:14:47.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:14:47.690 --> 00:14:50.030 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: You become this
magnet of information.

00:14:50.030 --> 00:14:52.660 align:middle line:84%
And then suddenly,
you realize, you know,

00:14:52.660 --> 00:14:54.050 align:middle line:90%
I cannot make up the story.

00:14:54.050 --> 00:14:56.180 align:middle line:84%
I have to go where
the information goes,

00:14:56.180 --> 00:14:57.187 align:middle line:90%
where the evidence goes.

00:14:57.187 --> 00:14:59.270 align:middle line:84%
And if you just let the
evidence speak for itself,

00:14:59.270 --> 00:15:00.350 align:middle line:90%
it writes itself.

00:15:00.350 --> 00:15:03.122 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, as it did here.

