>>SILVA: It just
takes 15 years to do.

00:15:04.705 --> 00:15:05.120 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: 15 years.

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:06.320 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Things are a bit
slow on this planet, you know.

00:15:06.320 --> 00:15:07.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, they are.

