00:22:39.650 --> 00:22:39.890 align:middle line:90%
bat--

00:22:39.890 --> 00:22:41.040 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Kind of
interesting, crazy.

00:22:41.040 --> 00:22:42.331 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, you know, crazy.

00:22:42.331 --> 00:22:44.240 align:middle line:84%
