00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:53.450 align:middle line:84%
At this point, I
had no intention

00:22:53.450 --> 00:22:55.283 align:middle line:84%
of going to the bloodline
story in the book,

00:22:55.283 --> 00:22:58.100 align:middle line:84%
but somehow the evidence began
to throw me in that direction.

00:22:58.100 --> 00:22:59.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because
they were grooming him

00:22:59.800 --> 00:23:01.000 align:middle line:90%
at such a deep level.

00:23:01.000 --> 00:23:01.800 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: Exactly.

00:23:01.800 --> 00:23:03.260 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: At such
a young age, they

00:23:03.260 --> 00:23:04.550 align:middle line:84%
must have known
something about him.

00:23:04.550 --> 00:23:06.260 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Exactly, and
he wasn't royalty.

00:23:06.260 --> 00:23:07.430 align:middle line:90%
So why was he a prince?

00:23:07.430 --> 00:23:08.604 align:middle line:90%
And he becomes a king.

00:23:08.604 --> 00:23:10.020 align:middle line:84%
Kind of like Godfrey
de Bouillion.

00:23:10.020 --> 00:23:12.350 align:middle line:84%
He wasn't royalty, but he
becomes king of Jerusalem,

00:23:12.350 --> 00:23:12.920 align:middle line:90%
which, of course, he denied.

00:23:12.920 --> 00:23:14.120 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But they identified
them, just like the--

00:23:14.120 --> 00:23:14.920 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: Exactly.

00:23:14.920 --> 00:23:17.390 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Exactly, like the
lamas identify other lamas.

00:23:17.390 --> 00:23:18.230 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: Exactly.

00:23:18.230 --> 00:23:20.840 align:middle line:84%
And there were other players as
well who at a very young age--

00:23:20.840 --> 00:23:22.020 align:middle line:84%
