00:32:53.790 --> 00:32:55.170 align:middle line:90%
means it's stone.

00:32:55.170 --> 00:32:58.414 align:middle line:84%
It's energy, and it's
light and nothing else.

00:32:58.414 --> 00:33:00.330 align:middle line:84%
And, of course, the
dimensions are pure sound.

00:33:00.330 --> 00:33:02.788 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But it is so elegant,
and it's just so beautiful.

00:33:02.788 --> 00:33:05.349 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: Oh, you breathe,
and it has a note to it.

00:33:05.349 --> 00:33:06.390 align:middle line:90%
And it comes back to you.

00:33:06.390 --> 00:33:08.471 align:middle line:84%
