00:33:12.360 --> 00:33:13.590 align:middle line:90%
>>SILVA: It really is.

00:33:13.590 --> 00:33:15.090 align:middle line:90%
And you start just humming.

00:33:15.090 --> 00:33:17.640 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, the
acoustics are so wonderful.

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:20.099 align:middle line:84%
And the Russians actually did
some experiments in buildings

00:33:20.099 --> 00:33:20.898 align:middle line:90%
