And they said that when you
stand in these buildings,

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:25.470 align:middle line:84%
in the Gothic cathedrals,
which, of course, are

00:33:25.470 --> 00:33:28.080 align:middle line:84%
an extension of Arabic design
that the Templars brought

00:33:28.080 --> 00:33:31.470 align:middle line:84%
into Europe, the first
skyscrapers in Europe.

00:33:31.470 --> 00:33:35.070 align:middle line:84%
The Russians found out
by studying the myths

00:33:35.070 --> 00:33:37.380 align:middle line:84%
that when you actually stand
a person inside the nave

00:33:37.380 --> 00:33:40.760 align:middle line:84%
