00:33:49.590 --> 00:33:51.030 align:middle line:90%
above normal waking state.

00:33:51.030 --> 00:33:53.820 align:middle line:84%
That's what the Templars
found under the Temple

00:33:53.820 --> 00:33:56.250 align:middle line:84%
Mount, the secret
recipe of how to create

00:33:56.250 --> 00:33:59.960 align:middle line:84%
a building on a specific piece
of land that elevates the soul.

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:03.990 align:middle line:84%
And Bernard knew about this
because where he lived,

00:34:03.990 --> 00:34:07.590 align:middle line:84%
he was also privy to
a group of mystics.

00:34:07.590 --> 00:34:09.500 align:middle line:90%
I think Rashi was one of them.

00:34:09.500 --> 00:34:12.823 align:middle line:84%
He was a Hebrew guy who was
fascinated with Kabbalah.

00:34:12.823 --> 00:34:14.489 align:middle line:84%
And they basically
exchanged information

00:34:14.489 --> 00:34:18.780 align:middle line:84%
about how to build a place that
allows you beyond meditation

00:34:18.780 --> 00:34:21.489 align:middle line:84%
to literally leave the body and
have an out-of-body experience

00:34:21.489 --> 00:34:23.489 align:middle line:84%
that makes you have a
personal experience of God

00:34:23.489 --> 00:34:25.230 align:middle line:90%
without an intermediary.

00:34:25.230 --> 00:34:27.540 align:middle line:84%
That's what the Templar
secret was all about.

00:34:27.540 --> 00:34:29.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And it was
