Any Gothic cathedral is.

00:35:03.960 --> 00:35:05.430 align:middle line:84%
But even so, the
Gothic cathedrals

00:35:05.430 --> 00:35:08.790 align:middle line:84%
are basically a
12th-century extrapolation

00:35:08.790 --> 00:35:10.350 align:middle line:90%
of the Great Pyramid.

00:35:10.350 --> 00:35:13.200 align:middle line:84%
So when you look at the
Great Pyramid, or Tiwanaku,

00:35:13.200 --> 00:35:17.700 align:middle line:84%
or Sacsayhuaman, Chichen
Itza, any sacred site you

00:35:17.700 --> 00:35:19.740 align:middle line:84%
