they are all built

00:35:19.740 --> 00:35:21.920 align:middle line:90%
on exactly the same recipe.

00:35:21.920 --> 00:35:24.270 align:middle line:84%
They just couldn't build
pyramids in the Middle Ages

00:35:24.270 --> 00:35:25.890 align:middle line:84%
