give the game away

00:35:25.890 --> 00:35:28.230 align:middle line:84%
that you're following
a heretical thought.

00:35:28.230 --> 00:35:30.470 align:middle line:90%
So they had to redesign it.

00:35:30.470 --> 00:35:33.190 align:middle line:84%
But ironically, the houses
of God that were eventually

00:35:33.190 --> 00:35:35.340 align:middle line:84%
dedicated to the Catholic
Church and Christianity

00:35:35.340 --> 00:35:38.757 align:middle line:84%
were borrowed from the
Arabs, their fiercest enemy.

00:35:38.757 --> 00:35:40.340 align:middle line:84%
It's a strange joke,
isn't it, really?

00:35:40.340 --> 00:35:41.210 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is.

00:35:41.210 --> 00:35:44.250 align:middle line:84%
>>SILVA: So any time you go
to any of these buildings,

00:35:44.250 --> 00:35:46.350 align:middle line:84%
