00:40:15.901 --> 00:40:17.650 align:middle line:84%
No, they didn't nail
the guy to the cross.

00:40:17.650 --> 00:40:18.900 align:middle line:90%
That's a symbol.

00:40:18.900 --> 00:40:21.060 align:middle line:10%
It's a metaphor of
the risen initiate,

00:40:21.060 --> 00:40:24.100 align:middle line:10%
